locality: South Africa, Eastern Cape, Storms River, SW corner of Kabbeljous Reserve (EVAGC) 800 m from gate. Valley thicket with Poaceae, 2 species of Mesembryanthemum and Aloe spp., in littoral zone with soil, well-drained quartizite sand. Full sun. Collected for Phytochemical Survey by NYBG/MRL.
